description:
"Contact24 is a system of automatic information retrieval and telephone trading of MBS, with a separate hotline number that allows customers to choose from various features and services. The hotline number is 19009088. By using Contact24, customers can:
- Automatically check account information: balance, matching order results for the day, notifications, and execution information of rights;
- Automatically change Contact24 password;
- Meet staff to place orders and check account information;
- Request support: retrieve Contact24 password automatically, support S24, support other information."
